	(753,1,'2015-12-28 05:46:15','2015-12-28 05:46:15','<h1 class=\"entry-title\">Find Commercial & Apartment Building Owners Likely to Sell</h1>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\nProspectNow is the ultimate tool for closing more real estate deals by finding owners who are most likely to sell or refinance.  ProspectNow has an online database of commercial and residential building owners that includes phone numbers, mailing addresses and building details.  Using ProspectNow\'s predictive analytics, we tag properties that have similar characteristics as properties that have actually sold in the recent past. \r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<h2>Commercial Property Database</h2>\r\nSearch more than 10 million commercial properties nationwide by location, size, property type, building details, LTV and more. Access owner mailing addresses and telephone numbers instantly. Use ProspectNow to add email addresses for your existing customers and relationships. Utilize the latest direct mailing tools to create targeted marketing campaigns and accumulate clients.\r\n<br>\r\n<a class=\"btn og\" href=\"search-commercial-real-estate\">Search Commercial Database</a>\r\n<h2>Residential Property Database</h2>\r\nWhether you want to contact expired, withdrawn, or FSBO listings, find phone numbers for owners of investment portfolios, or simply reach out to more potential sellers, ProspectNow is the ultimate tool for closing more real estate deals and finding buyers, sellers, or borrowers. ProspectNow has an online database of 100 million residential building owners that includes phone numbers, mailing addresses and property details.\r\n<br>\r\n<a class=\"btn og\" href=\"search-residential-real-estate\">Search Residential Database</a>\r\n<h2>Commercial Tenant Database</h2>\r\nSearch more than 30 million commercial tenants and companies nationwide. The ProspectNow tenant database can be used to target tenants and decision makers to help you close more deals. The tenant data includes data such as the annual sales, number of employees, key contacts, year founded, and the amount of space leased.\r\n\r\n<h2>Contact Management and Call Tracking</h2>\r\nProspectNow allows you to track the progress and sales activity of not just yourself, but your entire team of sales agents. The data and software are completely integrated, so your sales team can obtain thousands of leads while you are provided with the metrics necessary to measure your business success. The best part about the ProspectNow CRM tool is that you can integrate it however you like. You can have a team approach where all sales people see the same leads, or an individual approach where each salesperson only sees his or her own leads. ProspectNow is the only system on the market to date that provides leads, data feeds and contact management tools all in a single application. Just turn it on and start prospecting.\r\n\r\n<h2>Data File Downloads</h2>\r\nIf you already have a CRM you like to use, ProspectNow also offers a data export feature that allows you to download the data to Excel so you can load it into your CRM. For more information, Contact Us or call 888-956-9998.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"peach_background\">\r\n<b>Advanced Search Results</b>\r\n<img src=\"http://adarsh.prospectnow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/products-search-results.jpg\" alt=\"products-search-results\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:398px;\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Property Details</b>\r\n<img src=\"http://adarsh.prospectnow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/products-property-details.jpg\" alt=\"products-property-details\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:399px;\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-44\" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>','Products - Find Commercial and Apartment Building Owners','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2015-12-28 05:46:15','2015-12-28 05:46:15','',13,'http://staging.prospectnow.com/13-revision-v1/',0,'revis